videos.title: Pioneer Is Fun if 6-Crab Mill is Good
videos.description:
Has anybody told you that Pioneer is a fun format and that you should check it out? Well, every format is only as good as it's Mill deck. 

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish
